org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi.util

Class OsgiAdapterFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • AdapterFactoryImpl
      • org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi.util.OsgiAdapterFactory
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    OsgiItemProviderAdapterFactory

    public class OsgiAdapterFactory
extends AdapterFactoryImpl
    The Adapter Factory for the model. It provides an adapter createXXX method for each class of the model.
    See Also:
    OsgiPackage
